            <p><g type="sun-disc"/>
               <lb/>
               <choice><orig>Μνημῖον</orig><reg>Μνημεῖον</reg></choice> Σεούδα <choice><orig>Θ<unclear>α</unclear><lb break="no"/><unclear>δδέου</unclear></orig><reg>Θα<lb break="no"/>δδαίου</reg></choice>, παυσαμένη
